OL,5, Smart appliances could stop working    
OL,6, properly after just two years because  
OL,7, manufacturers are failing to provide   
OL,8, tech updates, according to Which?.     
OL,10,FResearch by the consumer champion found
OL,11,Fproducts like expensive dishwashers,   
OL,12,FTVs, and washing machines - which might
OL,13,Fbe expected to last more than a decade 
OL,14,F- are "being abandoned" by brands.     
OL,16,FA lack of software support from firms  
OL,17,Fmeans devices do not get updated.      
OL,19,FThe older they get, the risk of online 
OL,20,Fhacking also increases, Which? says.   
